rebuttal to https://www.medpagetoday.com/special-reports/exclusives/93166?xid=nl_popmed_2021-06-18&eun=g1647234d0r&utm_source=Sailthru&utm_medium=email&utm_campaign=PopMedicine_061821&utm_term=NL_Gen_Int_PopMedicine_Active

offit claims that vaccine adverse effects have always been found within 6 months. this is BS.
- Dengue ADE was detected after several years
- DTAP increased mortality in poor countries detected after decades
- inactivated measles vaccine (NOT MMR)

Looking more widely at medical inteventions :
(Vaccines are an anyway poorly-defined concept that enompass a very wide range of technologies from the attenuated replicating virus to inactivated whole viruses to virus fragments to now mrna, which is kind of a sumercomputer to manfacture any kind of protein. )
- butter by trans fat, vigorously promoted decades ago. now banned. https://twitter.com/TuckerGoodrich/status/1405905194475352067 (paper from 1950s promoting trans fats)
- vioxx heart attacks
- PPIs nutrient absorption problem

